! name: Homepage Relevance Filter
! description: Shows results found only on the main pages (homepages) of websites. Filters all results except those found strictly on second-level domain (SLD) pages with no subdomains and no subsequent URLs. So it only shows websites dedicated exclusively to what you are looking for.  
